Texts.Chs: 在一个古老的书卷上，我从其潦草的字迹中竟然找到了一个我们科学考察目标星球的坐标。让我试图呼叫考察团时，它们毫无回应，我应该快点通过S.A.I.L前往那里，调查究竟发生了什么事。
Texts.Eng: I've found an ancient text, and am alarmed. Scrawled within are coordinates that match up exactly with a ^orange;recent research expedition^reset; we sent out to the fringes. I get no response when hailing them. S.A.I.L can take me there.
There are no words to express the madness and strangeness that tugs now at the very roots of my soul. A piece of myself has been forever lost to that hellish place.
